# Canonical host: normalise www → apex so qesto.cc is the single indexable origin
# (avoids duplicate-content between www and non-www flagged by the SEO audit). Path
# and query are preserved via :splat. Note: this only fires if www.qesto.cc is bound
# as a custom domain on the Pages project; otherwise enforce it with a zone-level
# Redirect Rule instead.
https://www.qesto.cc/* https://qesto.cc/:splat 301

